===Noun===
'''photon''' (''plural'' '''photons''')
# {{particles}} The [[quantum]] of [[electromagnetic]] energy, regarded as a discrete [[particle]] having zero [[rest mass]], no electric charge, and an indefinitely long lifetime.  It is a [[gauge boson]].
